 Longhurst Ford]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Steven Ellery]]\n|align=\"left\"| [[Ford EF Falcon]]\n| \n| 161\n| style=\"background:#ffdf9f;\" | '''3rd'''\n| style=\"background:#ffdf9f;\" | '''3rd'''\n|- align=\"center\"\n! [[1997 Primus 1000 Classic|1997]]\n| 25\n|align=\"left\"| {{Flagicon|AUS}} [[Longhurst Racing|Castrol Longhurst Ford]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Charlie O'Brien (racing driver)|Charlie O'Brien]]\n|align=\"left\"| [[Ford EL Falcon]]\n| L1\n| 110\n| DNF\n| DNF\n|- align=\"center\"\n! [[1998 FAI 1000|1998]]\n| 25\n|align=\"left\"| {{Flagicon|AUS}} [[Longhurst Racing|Castrol Longhurst Ford]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Geoff Brabham]]\n|align=\"left\"| [[Ford EL Falcon]]\n| OC\n| 157\n| 8th\n| 8th\n|- align=\"center\"\n! [[1999 FAI 1000|1999]]\n| 25\n|align=\"left\"| {{Flagicon|AUS}} [[Longhurst Racing|Castrol Longhurst Ford]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Adam Macrow]]\n|align=\"left\"| [[Ford AU Falcon]]\n| \n| 150\n| DNF\n| DNF\n|- align=\"center\"\n! [[2000 FAI 1000|2000]]\n| 9\n|align=\"left\"| {{Flagicon|AUS}} [[Stone Brothers Racing]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|AUS}} [[David Besnard]]\n|align=\"left\"| [[Ford AU Falcon]]\n| \n| 151\n| DNF\n| DNF\n|- align=\"center\"\n! [[2001 V8 Supercar 1000|2001]]\n| 1\n|align=\"left\"| {{Flagicon|AUS}} [[Holden Racing Team]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Mark Skaife]]\n|align=\"left\"| [[Holden VX Commodore]]\n| \n| 161\n| style=\"background:#fbffbf;\"| '''1st'''\n| style=\"background:#fbffbf;\"| '''1st'''\n|- align=\"center\"\n! [[2002 Bob Jane T-Marts 1000|2002]]\n| 66\n|align=\"left\"| {{Flagicon|AUS}} [[Briggs Motor Sport|Team Betta Electrical]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Matthew White (racing driver)|Matthew White]]\n|align=\"left\"| [[Ford AU Falcon]]\n| \n| 161\n| 6th\n| 6th\n|- align=\"center\"\n! [[2003 Bob Jane T-Marts 1000|2003]]\n| 2\n|align=\"left\"| {{Flagicon|AUS}} [[Holden Racing Team]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{Flagicon|NZL}} [[Jim Richards (