0|2003]]\n| 2\n|align=\"left\"| {{Flagicon|AUS}} [[Holden Racing Team]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{Flagicon|NZL}} [[Jim Richards (racing driver)|Jim Richards]]\n|align=\"left\"| [[Holden VY Commodore]]\n| \n| 161\n| 5th\n| 5th\n|- align=\"center\"\n! [[2004 Bob Jane T-Marts 1000|2004]]\n| 8\n|align=\"left\"| {{Flagicon|AUS}} [[Perkins Engineering]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{Flagicon|AUS}} [[Paul Dumbrell]]\n|align=\"left\"| [[Holden VY Commodore]]\n| \n| 129\n| DNF\n| DNF\n|- align=\"center\"\n! [[2005 Supercheap Auto 1000|2005]]\n| 44\n|align=\"left\"| {{Flagicon|AUS}} [[Team Dynamik]]<br>{{Flagicon|AUS}} [[Longhurst Racing]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{Flagicon|BRA}} [[Max Wilson]]\n|align=\"left\"| [[Holden VZ Commodore]]\n| \n| 32\n| DNF\n| DNF\n|- align=\"center\"\n! [[2006 Supercheap Auto Bathurst 1000|2006]]\n| 55\n|align=\"left\"| {{Flagicon|AUS}} [[Rod Nash Racing]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{Flagicon|AUS}} [[Steve Owen (racing driver)|Steve Owen]]\n|align=\"left\"| [[Holden VZ Commodore]]\n| \n| 161\n| 7th\n| 7th\n|}\n\n===Complete Sandown Endurance results===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center; font-size:90%\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Team\n! Co-Drivers\n! Car\n! Class\n! Laps\n! Overall<br>Position\n! Class<br>Position\n|-\n! [[1984 Castrol 500|1984]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|AUS}} [[JPS Team BMW]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|NZL}} [[Jim Richards (racing driver)|Jim Richards]]\n|align=\"left\"| [[BMW E24|BMW 635 CSi]]\n| Over 3000cc\n| 72\n| DNF\n| DNF\n|-\n! [[1985 Castrol 500|1985]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|AUS}} [[JPS Team BMW]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|NZL}} [[Jim Richards (racing driver)|Jim Richards]]\n|align=\"left\"| [[BMW E24|BMW 635 CSi]]\n| A\n| 129\n| style=\"background:#fbffbf;\"| '''1st'''\n| style=\"background:#fbffbf;\"| '''1st'''\n|-\n! [[1986 Castrol 500|1986]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|AUS}} [[JPS Team BMW]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|NZL}} [[Jim Richards (racing driver)|Jim Richards]]\n|align=\"left\"| [[BMW E24|BMW 635 CSi]]\n| B\n| 127\n