con]]\n| \n| 151\n| 10th\n| 10th\n|-\n! [[1998 Tickford 500|1998]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{Flagicon|AUS}} [[Longhurst Racing|Castrol Longhurst Ford]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{Flagicon|AUS}} [[Geoff Brabham]]\n|align=\"left\"| [[Ford EL Falcon]]\n| \n| 7\n| DNF\n| DNF\n|-\n! [[2003 Betta Electrical Sandown 500|2003]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{Flagicon|AUS}} [[Holden Racing Team]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|NZL}} [[Jim Richards (racing driver)|Jim Richards]]\n|align=\"left\"| [[Holden VY Commodore]]\n| \n| 140\n| 10th\n| 10th\n|-\n! [[2004 Betta Electrical Sandown 500|2004]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{Flagicon|AUS}} [[Perkins Engineering|Castrol Perkins Racing]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Paul Dumbrell]]\n|align=\"left\"| [[Holden VY Commodore]]\n| \n| 159\n| 8th\n| 8th\n|-\n! [[2007 Just Car Insurance 500|2007]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{Flagicon|AUS}} [[Holden Racing Team]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Glenn Seton]]\n|align=\"left\"| [[Holden VE Commodore]]\n| \n| 160\n| 13th\n| 13th\n|}\n\n===Complete Bathurst 12 Hour results===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:90%\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Team\n! Co-Drivers\n! Car\n! Class\n! Laps\n! Overall<br>Position\n! Class<br>Position\n|- align=\"center\"\n! [[1992 James Hardie 12 Hour|1992]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|AUS}} [[BMW]] Australia Pty Ltd\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Alan Jones (racing driver)|Alan Jones]]<br>{{flagicon|NZL}} [[Neville Crichton]]\n|align=\"left\"| [[BMW E34|BMW M5]]\n| C\n| 251\n| style=\"background:#dfdfdf;\"| '''2nd'''\n| style=\"background:#fbffbf;\"| '''1st'''\n|- align=\"center\"\n! [[2009 WPS Bathurst 12 Hour|2009]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|AUS}} [[TMR Australia]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Rod Salmon]]<br>{{flagicon|AUS}} [[Damien White]]\n|align=\"left\"| [[Mitsubishi Lancer Evolution|Mitsubishi Lancer RS Evo X]]\n| C\n| 239\n| style=\"background:#fbffbf;\"| '''1st'''\n| style=\"background:#fbffbf;\"| '''1st'''\n|- align=\"center\"\n! [[2017 Liqui Moly Bathurst 12 Hour|2017]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|AUS}} BMW Team SRM\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|GER}} [[Timo Glock]]<br>{{flagicon|AUS}} [[Mark Skaife]]<br>{{flagicon|AUS}} [[Russell Ingall]]\n|align=\"left\"| [[BMW M6 GT3]]\n| AP\n| 134\n| DNF\n| DNF\n|- align=\"center\"\n! [[2018 Liqui Moly Bathurst 12 Hour|2018]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Longhurst Racing|Boat Works Racing]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Matthew Brabham]]<br>{{flagicon|AUS}} Aaron Seton\n|align=\"left\"| [[BMW M4]] GT4\n| C\n| 250\n| 22nd\n| style=\"background:#fbffbf;\"| '''1st'''\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{S-start}}\n{{S-sports}}\n{{Succession box| before = [[Peter Brock]]<br>[[David Parsons (racing driver)|David Parsons]]<br>[[Peter McLeod]] | title = Winner of the [[Bathurst 1000]] | years = 1988<br>(with [[Tomas Mezera]]) | after = [[Dick Johnson (racing driver)|Dick Johnson]]<br>[[John Bowe (racing driver)|John Bowe]]}}\n{{Succession box| before = Peter Doulman | title = Winner of the [[Australian Super Touring Championship|Australian Manufacturers' Championship]] | years = [[1994 Australian Manufacturers' Championship|1994]] | after = [[Paul Morris (motorsport)|Paul Morris]]}}\n{{Succession box| before = [[Garth Tander]]<br>[[Jason Bargwanna]] | title = Winner of the [[Bathurst 1000]] | years = 2001<br>(with [[Mark Skaife]]) | after = [[Mark Skaife]]<br>[[Jim Richards (racing driver)|Jim Richards]]}}\n{{succession box | before = [[Graham Alexander (racing driver)|Graham Alexander]] <br> [[Rod Salmon]] <br> [[Damien White]] | title = [[Bathurst 12 Hour|Winner of the Bathurst 12 Hour]] | years = [[2009 WPS Bathurst 12 Hour|2009]] <br> (with [[Rod Salmon]] & [[Damien White]]) | after = [[John Bowe (racing driver)|John Bowe]] <br> [[Garry Holt]] <br> [[Paul Morris (racing driver)|Paul Morris]]}}\n{{S-end}}\n\n{{Bathurst 1000 winners}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Longhurst, Tony}}\n[[Category:1957 births]]\n[[Category:Australian racing drivers]]\n[[Category:Australian Touring Car Champion